OL,3,CVisually impaired veteran to run from
OL,4,CLands End and John O'Groats
OL,6,FDarren has previously ran the London
OL,7,Fmarathon and Boston marathon but says
OL,8,Fthe "End to End" will be his toughest
OL,9,Ftest of endurance yet.
OL,11,FDarren is hoping to raise thousands of
OL,12,Fpounds for the Visually Impaired
OL,13,FVeterans Ski Club, an organisation
OL,14,Fthat hopes to rehabilitate and re-
OL,15,Fbuild confidence in veterans with
OL,16,Fsight loss.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Darren Blanks,
OL,19,Fsaid: "Everyday when running is
OL,20,Fdifferent, the terrain could be
OL,21,Fdifferent.
