OL,3,CVisually impaired veteran to run from
OL,4,CLands End and John O'Groats
OL,6,FHowever, it was after he returned home
OL,7,Fto Egremont and starting working as a
OL,8,Fpostman that his health started to
OL,9,Fdecline.
OL,11,FHe said: "It was just one day that I
OL,12,Fstarted to have problems with my
OL,13,Fvision and it was discovered that I
OL,14,Fhad a brain tumour.
OL,16,F"When the tumour was removed it left
OL,17,Fme deaf in my left ear and by the age
OL,18,Fof 23 I had hearing and vision loss.
